import { Box, Button, Center, Flex, Icon, Image, Spacer, Text, } from "@chakra-ui/react";
// import phoneimg from "../../images/phone.png"
import shrek from "../../images/shrek.jfif"
import esh from "../../images/esh.jfif"
import fiona from "../../images/Fiona.png"
import fandom from "../../images/fandom.webp"
import feya from "../../images/feya.png"
import godfather from "../../images/godfather.png"
import alpachino from "../../images/alpachino.png"
import hz from "../../images/hz.png"
import fredo from "../../images/fredo.png"
import sonny from "../../images/sonny.png"

function shrek1() {
   display="block"
  }
export default function Header() {
    const [displayStyle, setDisplayStyle] = useState('none'); // Изначально устанавливаем стиль на "none"

    const shrek1 = () => {
        setDisplayStyle('block'); // Функция изменяет состояние, чтобы показать изображение
    };
    return (
        <>
            <Box mt="90" ml="400" bg="green" width="700px" height="620px">
                <Box>
                    <Text fontSize="50px" fontWeight="1000" fontFamily="Libre Baskerville" pt="6" textAlign="center" color="white">Memory game</Text>
                </Box>
                <Flex justifyContent="space-between" wrap="wrap" p="6">
                    <Box display="flex" justifyContent="center" alignItems="center" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                        <Image id="shrek"  onClick={shrek1} width="110px" height="90px" src={shrek}  style={{ display: displayStyle }} // Динамически устанавливаем стиль отображения изображения
/>
                    </Box>
                    <Box bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                        <Image display="none" width="110px" height="90px" src={esh}/>
                    </Box>
                    <Box bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                        <Image display="none" mt="1" width="110px" height="90px" src={fiona}/>
                    </Box>
                    <Box bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                        <Image display="none" ml="2" width="110px" height="90px" src={fandom}/>
                    </Box>
                    <Box bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" width="110px" height="90px" src={feya}/>
                    </Box>

                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" width="110px" height="90px" src={godfather}/>
                    </Box>
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" width="190px" height="80px" src={alpachino}/>
                    </Box> 
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" ml="-2" width="190px" height="80px" src={hz}/>
                    </Box>
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" ml="1" width="110px" height="80px" src={fredo}/>
                    </Box>
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" ml="1" width="110px" height="80px" src={sonny}/>
                    </Box>

                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" ml="1" width="110px" height="80px" src={sonny}/>
                    </Box>
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" width="110px" height="90px" src={godfather}/>
                    </Box>
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" ml="1" width="110px" height="80px" src={fredo}/>
                    </Box>
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" width="110px" height="90px" src={fiona}/>
                    </Box>
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" width="110px" height="90px" src={esh}/>
                    </Box>
                    
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" width="110px" height="90px" src={shrek}/>
                    </Box>
                    <Box  mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" width="190px" height="80px" src={alpachino}/>

                    </Box>
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" width="110px" height="90px" src={feya}/>

                    </Box>
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" ml="1" width="110px" height="80px" src={fredo}/>

                    </Box>
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px">
                    <Image display="none" mt="1" ml="-2" width="190px" height="80px" src={hz}/>

                    </Box>

                </Flex>
            </Box>
        </>

    )
}
